{"type": "article", "id": 17920, "title": "Bud Light 易拉罐设计", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-23T06:53:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104225mMFbodQApN5DKIf6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t百威清啤 Bud Light 为了今年的 Mad Decent Block Party，邀请奥地利设计师 Daniel Triendl 设计了一组限量版的易拉罐。罐身可见用油画式的笔触书写的线条或字母，厚重且含有丰富的颜色，显得张扬大胆，契合年轻人。或者使用像素化的图像，在颜色的撞击中带来一种时尚感。<a href=\"http://danieltriendl.com/Bud-Light-Mad-Decent-Block-Party\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144945Mj7RrHCxsKhtbZqF.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144946EmaGLCBn6P5fqXkr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"804\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145102IDrWJscfw87GtBO0.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"372\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145104WOLlUh5u89D3HJ0B.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"804\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145105qpHbrZE216Szsuvy.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1223\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.13240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}